{"tid":412346,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU翻唱碟延遲推出 和原唱者懷疑被殺有關","createTime":"2017-09-24T14:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T14:47:36.000Z","uid":34643,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c21e19c00dca677850bc74ab6a997ad3a3458b9d","tid":412346,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:35:49.000Z","msg":"現年24歲的韓國女歌手IU今日在首爾梨花大學舉行出道9周年粉絲見面會。IU在兩個小時的見面會中，獻唱了翻唱專輯《花書籤2》的幾首歌曲，她還翻唱了已故歌王金光石的名歌《抱着要忘記的心》，以及播出相關的MV。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DKfuCVNUIAEEVH6.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDKfuCVNUIAEEVH6.jpg%3Aorig&h=4c98b844&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而IU原定明天推出這張翻唱專輯，但因要臨時抽起其中一曲而推遲至中秋假期才可以面世，事務所今日發聲明向粉絲致歉。IU在見面會上亦親自為此致歉，並解釋說自己一直以來也是金光石前輩的粉絲，所以一直希望可以翻唱金光石的《抱着要忘記的心》這首歌曲。<br />\n<br />\n不過，因為最近一部有關金光石的紀錄片在韓國上映，執導紀錄片的導演懷疑金光石當年並非自殺而是被殺，令他再次成為新聞熱話，故IU透露將原本翻唱專輯中收錄了金光石這首歌曲抽起了，她認為聽音樂的時候，不可以單純地只聽歌曲，而是會因外在因素影響聽音樂的心情，故她認為在這陣子，大家聽到她翻唱金光石這首歌時，心情不會舒服，所以決定抽起這首歌曲，並希望待大家可以懷着開心的心情去聽這首歌時，她才收錄此曲的翻唱版本。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DKfuCVKUMAAeasR.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDKfuCVKUMAAeasR.jpg%3Aorig&h=31e60f6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5d86cff90e33ca37e02f394f6f9e7559991d9a7","tid":412346,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:52:02.000Z","msg":"主打歌呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀"},{"pid":"350738ec27d3ed5558d9e7d11afe1a703e442893","tid":412346,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMgy1fjuzusgry1j30u011i41l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMgy1fjuzusgry1j30u011i41l.jpg&h=14b1395e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f058d30a816fe2c351f17c836ed0b182df1b310","tid":412346,"uid":43880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:47:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>主打歌呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀</blockquote><br />\n本來嘅主打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a8dda385f67173248a457b27b5d2b57c2026bd","tid":412346,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:55:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>主打歌呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀呀</blockquote><br />\n本來嘅主打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係, teaser3果首, 本身諗住同夜信呼應, 同埋呢種曲風應該好岩佢唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb1e78fe4dda9bd132765540b0b5ca232807dfe","tid":412346,"uid":34643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Rxae2lj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRxae2lj.jpg&h=b99bc98a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"543f3370191b1822c0be1ab0f0a0ce360a596416","tid":412346,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:25:03.000Z","msg":"本來這支MV實拍給，翻唱的金光石-잊어야 한다는 마음으로的，歌也已經早早就錄好了，但是由於最近的新聞，怎麼都覺得不適合在這個時機發出來，於是決定不在這張專輯收錄，也因為這個導致專輯推遲出廠，一直在道歉。 ​"},{"pid":"3f46cfda9d807a786460985a1d672dddd23d83e2","tid":412346,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:47:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/98279\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F98279&d=XSbuDkYM8s2eWeda%2FQGdIE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=d0cc5ef1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/98279</a>"}]}